Job Description

  Implementation and deploying of SIEM solution
  SIEM Solution – Splunk, Qradar, ArcSight and NetWitness
  Basic project management skill to work/liaise with product vendors, partners and customers
  Provide informal training to partners and customers

Requirements

  Diploma/Degree in Computer Engineering, Computer Science, Information Systems or equivalent
  Minimum 4-5 years of relevant work experience in IT security implementation and deployment
  Minimum 2 year of relevant work experience with SIEM solution
  Good understanding in operating system technology, such as Unix, Linux and Windows Server
  Familiar with Virtualization such as VMWare, Microsoft HyperV, Oracle Box
  Good networking knowledge
  Technically inclined and hands on
  Good interpersonal skills, independent, pro-active and a team player
  Good presentation and writing skills

